---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Like one activity record

Usage: like [OPTIONS] <ACTIVITY_ID>

Arguments:
  <ACTIVITY_ID>
          Canonical activity ID

Options:
      --yes
          Skip only the final default-No confirmation

      --dry-run
          Complete preflight and show details without liking the activity

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

The command performs an authoritative activity preflight and never retries automatically. Exit code 3 means the like outcome must be verified independently.
